title: Boston Tea Party
overview: Boston Tea Party features Filip & Fredrik. The name is taken from the Tea Party in Boston. The program sets the duo questions you may not have always wondered about. eg Does a dachshound recognize his brother? How do you prepare a man for best flavor? Together with both known and unknown people and the all-knowing "Super Femman" discusses Filip & Fredrik everything from animals to cannibalism and terrorism. "Super Femman" consist of five experts, current political scientist Stig-Björn Ljunggren, psychologist Anna Karlstedt, historian Bengt Liljegren, physician Mikael Sandström and physicist Patrik Norqvist with the popular element "Veckans macka".
